    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Peel and finely slice the <strong>brown&nbsp;onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>Slice the <strong>portobello mushrooms</strong></p>",
