    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>pork</strong> is brown, transfer it to a bowl and return the pan to a medium heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong></p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>sliced onion</strong> and <strong>mushroom</strong> and cook for 6-7 min or until starting to caramelise</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong>&nbsp;and cook for 1 min further</p>",
